{"tid":2099091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舊時《老夫子》打中國人　已指出中國想征服世界","createTime":"2020-07-08T03:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T04:31:32.000Z","uid":261647,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d3db7ced3d614918738f7bb49a1a2a11eb6b97a0","tid":2099091,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbiXyGFVcAEfhM1?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEbiXyGFVcAEfhM1%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=a4c8837a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上世紀的事。世界對中國的看法主要兩個，前期是，神秘古老祥和會功夫並有很多小數民族的老朋友，後期是，殺手和軍隊、軍事。不過香港人早期認知，雖然後來遺忘，但可能才接近真實。這是《老夫子》漫畫，當中象徵中國的中國人說了兩句話「我們五年趕上英國、十年追上美帝！」「三十年後征服世界！」<br />\n<br />\n圖中的中國人除了口講「我們五年趕上英國、十年追上美帝！」「三十年後征服世界！」，他左手臂也寫了字，是「殺人」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276943014489780225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1276943014489780225&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=03c4b368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1276943014489780225&h=2d02b393\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1276943014489780225</a>"},{"pid":"d1730f2eac78eebfadfbb7befe799bbc35430a72","tid":2099091,"uid":120148,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"圖2隻腳仲要係豬蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37017e483129f5fd197df632c3e584c99b5021b8","tid":2099091,"uid":331973,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"老夫子作者犯國安法，拉得"},{"pid":"b99e9b8e40c2ca4b736f1c9829ef54ae6c192aac","tid":2099091,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37017e483129f5fd197df632c3e584c99b5021b8","tid":2099091,"uid":331973,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":